11#ifndef PC_AUDIO_TRACK_H_
12#define PC_AUDIO_TRACK_H_
13
14#include <string>
15
16#include "api/media_stream_interface.h"
17#include "api/media_stream_track.h"
18#include "api/scoped_refptr.h"
19#include "api/sequence_checker.h"
20
21namespace webrtc {
22
23class AudioTrack : public MediaStreamTrack<AudioTrackInterface>,
24 public ObserverInterface {
25 protected:
26 // Protected ctor to force use of factory method.
27 AudioTrack(const std::string& label,
28 const rtc::scoped_refptr<AudioSourceInterface>& source);
29
30 AudioTrack() = delete;
31 AudioTrack(const AudioTrack&) = delete;
32 AudioTrack& operator=(const AudioTrack&) = delete;
33
34 ~AudioTrack() override;
35
36 public:
37 static rtc::scoped_refptr<AudioTrack> Create(
38 const std::string& id,
39 const rtc::scoped_refptr<AudioSourceInterface>& source);
40
41 // MediaStreamTrack implementation.
42 std::string kind() const override;
43
44 private:
45 // AudioTrackInterface implementation.
46 AudioSourceInterface* GetSource() const override;
47
48 void AddSink(AudioTrackSinkInterface* sink) override;
49 void RemoveSink(AudioTrackSinkInterface* sink) override;
50
51 // ObserverInterface implementation.
52 void OnChanged() override;
53
54 private:
55 const rtc::scoped_refptr<AudioSourceInterface> audio_source_;
56 SequenceChecker thread_checker_;
57};
58
59} // namespace webrtc
60
61#endif // PC_AUDIO_TRACK_H_
